cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a novel sparse learning based feature selection method for linear classification models, which is a common topic in machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the optimization algorithm and provides experimental results, which are relevant to cs.AI and cs.DS. Finally, the proposed method can be applied to various datasets and tasks, which is related to cs.NE.
